      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "十架到了！因为所有"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "忠魂都当经加略；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我们在此同祂蒙羞，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "不肯自怜，不退却；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "因为不过一点时候，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我们如此感苦痛；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "将来见祂，一切忧愁，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "要消在祂笑容中。"
            }
          ]
        }
