      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我们努力向竿而前，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "日近一日仍追随；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我们已经仿佛能见"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "天城四射的光辉；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我们已经隐约可闻"
